name: Socio-Economic and Educational Development Society ( SEEDS)

address: No. 6/1156/2, JK Complex, EB Colony, Paramathy Road, Namakkal

briefDescription: SEEDS is a voluntary and grassroot NGO based in Tamilnadu, India. It was registered in 1994 as Society under Tamilnadu Societies Registration Act 1975 and With FCRA 1976 IN 2002 and with Income Tax Act 1961,12AA and 80G. Primary Target groups of the organisation are women, children and youths of disadvantaged and marginalized communities in rural and tribal areas, elsewhere in Tamilnadu, India. SEEDS collaborates with various like minded organisations, departments, institutions and individual, both government and non-government of International and National communities.
